metadata.name: WhosBuilding #01
metadata.description:
WhosBuilding #01

1/1 3840px x 3840px png

WhosBuilding #01 is a manually created 3d art pattern using GeometryNodes and Python. 

Together these base building models create a unique art pattern; And this unique piece if of 1 of 49 of these patterns, which contribute to the collection "WhosBuilding".

The art comes with the original high-resolution .png format document, and the 4K resolution .png format document; And early access to future collections.
